  "detailed_description": "<h1>Is this Game Trying to Kill Me? is coming soon!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/6eed6cfd95ba91005b6ddc2b761b688d.webp?t=1732013377\" width=480 height=60 /></span><br>In this game, you are a mercenary who was assigned to find a missing person. One of the Archmages of the Academy broke the communication when he was conducting his research in the depths of the Infected Territory. At one time this area had been exposed to the monstrous amount of magic, and it is filled now with creatures of the Abyss. Go on the trail of the missing Archmage and plunge into the atmosphere of an adventure full of magic and dangers!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/9f76547e540516f0ab00cdd7ac85558d.webp?t=1732013377\" width=480 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore ancient ruins, mysterious caves and abandoned houses;<br></li><li>Fight with magical creatures;<br></li><li>Collect items and use them to solve puzzles;<br></li><li>Create alchemical potions from the magic plants you found;<br></li><li>Open the passageway between the worlds and find the legendary artifact!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/1ae55bb60eb751e457ec09ce5bfabad2.poster.avif?t=1732013377\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/1ae55bb60eb751e457ec09ce5bfabad2.webm?t=1732013377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/1ae55bb60eb751e457ec09ce5bfabad2.mp4?t=1732013377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/6eed6cfd95ba91005b6ddc2b761b688d.webp?t=1732013377\" width=480 height=60 /></span><br>In this game, you are a mercenary who was assigned to find a missing person. One of the Archmages of the Academy broke the communication when he was conducting his research in the depths of the Infected Territory. At one time this area had been exposed to the monstrous amount of magic, and it is filled now with creatures of the Abyss. Go on the trail of the missing Archmage and plunge into the atmosphere of an adventure full of magic and dangers!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/9f76547e540516f0ab00cdd7ac85558d.webp?t=1732013377\" width=480 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore ancient ruins, mysterious caves and abandoned houses;<br></li><li>Fight with magical creatures;<br></li><li>Collect items and use them to solve puzzles;<br></li><li>Create alchemical potions from the magic plants you found;<br></li><li>Open the passageway between the worlds and find the legendary artifact!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/1ae55bb60eb751e457ec09ce5bfabad2.poster.avif?t=1732013377\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/1ae55bb60eb751e457ec09ce5bfabad2.webm?t=1732013377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1215280/extras/1ae55bb60eb751e457ec09ce5bfabad2.mp4?t=1732013377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
